{"tid":692304,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【瘋搶二千萬樓】柏蔚山247伙近沽清吸金58億 投資客佔兩成","createTime":"2018-06-06T13:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T14:42:42.000Z","uid":68476,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c638e32ca3b65a168209cf54b8c9205552be23f","tid":692304,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"【瘋搶二千萬樓】柏蔚山247伙近沽清吸金58億 投資客佔兩成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528289392_fc53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528289392_fc53.jpg&h=80a89192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528288667_05b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528288667_05b5.jpg&h=a2a17d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界(017)表示，旗下北角柏蔚山收票約6天收約1,800個登記，今展開首輪銷售涉247伙，截止下午8時30分共售出237伙，佔首批可售單位約96%，共套現約58億元，為本年度首輪銷售套現金額最高新盤，平均成交價總值逾2,400萬元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，大手組別錄27組買家購入兩伙單位或以上，共沽57伙，其中錄1組內地大手買家斥8,727.6萬元掃4伙三房戶，平均每伙成交價均逾2,000萬元。客源分布方面，據悉，買家以用家及換樓客為主，八成為用家，兩成為投資者；港島客佔七成，而九龍客佔兩成。<br />\n<br />\n市場反應極度熱烈，發展商對項目銷情相當滿意，會視乎市場反應及收票情況，與合作夥伴研究及商討，積極考慮短期內提價加推單位，料部分單位將有雙位數字提價幅度，最快下周展開次輪銷售。"},{"pid":"9055d2318731ae566d43631c5b6e08ffb5b751c2","tid":692304,"uid":49830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"又升"},{"pid":"ead052c7207f7acb1709e53fc6f31c05355b737e","tid":692304,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"土地供應不足喎 公私營要平衡喎"},{"pid":"413c83de8250691c82f8e6eb1b9125cbb783ad38","tid":692304,"uid":68476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:10:07.000Z","msg":"D 樓唔使錢架，狗衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c79ed7eaa27f2c514999cbb6c2b44738b69e10b","tid":692304,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"f6e88a46c7c744551945624aa2694a50228e3634","tid":692304,"uid":96896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"乜香港有窮人嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32a5875c024e20eacb50f27082649658d6d613c","tid":692304,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6e88a46c7c744551945624aa2694a50228e3634","tid":692304,"uid":96896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"乜香港有窮人嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"有東方 冇窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}